AppleCameraAssistant(8)     System Manager's Manual    AppleCameraAssistant(8)

NAME
     AppleCameraAssistant – CoreMediaIO DAL Assistant Process.

DESCRIPTION
     AppleCameraAssistant is used by the CoreMediaIO Device Abstraction Layer
     Plug-In that provides video capture from some models of Apple FaceTime
     cameras using AVFoundation Capture APIs.  The process allows multiple
     applications to simultaneously capture from the same camera.

